name: WARFARm
description: WARFARm is a real time strategy farm game. Your Goal is to earn more Money in 7 days than your neighbour. Therefor you can buy different kinds of plants - with different abilities - to defend your other plants from the zombies your neighbour sends at night. THIS IS A VERY VERY EARLY VERSION - If you find bugs you can leave a short message in the comments to help me fix them :) Thanks for playing!
